Title: Sweetums
Plot: The Parks Department forms a partnership with a local company to sell energy bars at the parks in Pawnee, but Leslie tries to stop the deal when she discovers how unhealthy the snacks are. Mark reluctantly agrees to help Tom move out of his house.
GuestStars: Justin Theroux, Phil Reeves, Don McManus, Jim O'Heir, Retta, Jama Williamson, Gary Weeks
